data.description: **Home back on market at no fault of the home. Buyer could not perform** Welcome to your new home, a stunning residence nestled within Beaverton's sought-after Westbrook planned unit development. This charming home has undergone a complete transformation, boasting new flooring, fresh paint, upgraded cabinets, and pristine countertops. It's a true gem waiting for its new owners to move right in and enjoy. The Westbrook HOA offers a wealth of amenities to enhance your lifestyle, all included in your HOA fee, including lush greenspace that is professionally maintained, two pools, one for adult-only use, a clubhouse with versatile space for gathering or events and a community garden where you can excercise your green thumb! Seller to offer up to $10,000 towards a rate buy down or closing costs.
